Symbol.Script_VL:
values "type_spec" "Металл", "Изделие" ! ============================================================================== ! General Dimensions ! ==============================================================================
call "railParameterControl_mod" parameters all !parameters hr = 1050/1000 parameters hrw = 60/1000 parameters hrh = 40/1000 parameters pth = 50/1000 parameters pw = 50/1000 parameters bth = 10/1000 parameters bw = 40/1000 parameters nb = 1 !parameters hroL = 50/1000 !parameters hroR = 50/1000 values "type_ogrtxt" "Серийная площадка", "Сверху на бетон", "Сбоку на бетон", "Сверху на металл", "Сбоку на металл"
if type_ogrtxt = "Серийная площадка" then parameters type_ogr = 1 ttxt = "-Ш " parameters gs_PostBaseOverhang = 140/1000 endif
if type_ogrtxt = "Сверху на бетон" then parameters type_ogr = 2 ttxt = "-ВБ " parameters gs_PostBaseOverhang = 10/1000 endif
if type_ogrtxt = "Сбоку на бетон" then parameters type_ogr = 3 ttxt = "-ББ " parameters gs_PostBaseOverhang = 190/1000 endif
if type_ogrtxt = "Сверху на металл" then parameters type_ogr = 4 ttxt = "-ВМ " parameters gs_PostBaseOverhang = 10/1000 endif
if type_ogrtxt = "Сбоку на металл" then parameters type_ogr = 5 ttxt = "-БМ " parameters gs_PostBaseOverhang = 100/1000 endif
values "mat_pokr" "тип 1","тип 2","тип 3","тип 4" if not(mun_subpos) then if rom = "Нет наклона" then parameters subpos = "ОГ" + ttxt + str("%.0m",(hr+0.14+0.01)*100) + "."+ str("%.0m",lrah*100) parameters naen = "Ограждение " + subpos parameters tip_profile = "Ограждение ОГ"+ttxt else parameters subpos = "ОГЛ" + ttxt + str("%.0",ani) + "."+ str("%.0m",(hr+0.14+0.01)*100)+ "." + str("%.0m",lrah*100) parameters naen = "Ограждение лестничное " + subpos parameters tip_profile = "Ограждение лестничное ОГЛ"+ttxt endif endif
! ============================================================================== ! Structural Dimensions ! ============================================================================== parameters pd=pw,pth=pw parameters bd=bw,bth=bw lock "pd","bd","pth","bth"
dim stHandrailType[2] stHandrailType[1] = `Прямоугольные` stHandrailType[2] = `Круглые`
parameters hrt = stHandrailType[1] values "hrt_m" 1, 2
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "hrt" then hrt_m = 1 if hrt = stHandrailType[2] then hrt_m = 2 parameters hrt_m = hrt_m else hrt = stHandrailType[1] if hrt_m = 2 then hrt = stHandrailType[2] parameters hrt = hrt endif
dim stPostType[2] stPostType[1] = `Прямоугольные` stPostType[2] = `Круглые`
values "pt" stPostType values "pt_m" 1, 2
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "pt" then pt_m = 1 if pt = stPostType[2] then pt_m = 2 parameters pt_m = pt_m else pt = stPostType[1] if pt_m = 2 then pt = stPostType[2] parameters pt = pt endif
dim stBarType[2] stBarType[1] = `Прямоугольные` stBarType[2] = `Круглые`
values "bt" stBarType values "bt_m" 1, 2
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "bt" then bt_m = 1 if bt = stBarType[2] then bt_m = 2 parameters bt_m = bt_m else bt = stBarType[1] if bt_m = 2 then bt = stBarType[2] parameters bt = bt endif
if ptyp_m <> 1 then if hrt_m = 1 then values "b" hrw if hrt_m = 2 then values "b" hrd lock "a","b","zzyzx" hideparameter "LengthSize" else if hrt_m = 1 then if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "hrw" then B = hrw parameters B = B else hrw = B parameters hrw = hrw endif else if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "hrd" then B = hrd parameters B = B else hrd = B parameters hrd = hrd endif endif
lock "a","zzyzx" endif
! ====================================================================== ! UI ! ======================================================================
call "ui_tabcontrol" parameters controlType = 1, nTabs = 10, gs_ui_current_page = gs_ui_current_page
Symbol.Script_3D:
del top if rom = "Нет наклона" then material fmat txh = 0 tzh = ds HOTSPOT lrah-hroR, txh, tzh, 9991, addr2, 1+128 HOTSPOT lrah+addr2-hroR, txh, tzh, 9992, addr2, 2 HOTSPOT lrah-1-hroR,txh,tzh,9993,addr2,3
HOTSPOT hroL, txh, tzh, 9994, addl2, 1+128 HOTSPOT -addl2+hroL, txh, tzh, 9995, addl2, 2 HOTSPOT 1+hroL,txh,tzh,9996,addl2,3 addy -pd/2-0.003 addx hroL-addl2 addz ds BRICK l_4,0.003, 0.14 endif
Symbol.Script_2D: if GLOB_CONTEXT=6 then call "rail" parameters tip_profile_1=tip_profile_1, tip_profile_2=tip_profile_2, tip_profile_3=tip_profile_3, tip_profile_4=tip_profile_4, rom=rom end endif
Symbol.Script_1D:
show = 0 call "Показ_по_сборкам" PARAMETERS ALL subpos=subpos, pos=GLOB_ID RETURNED_PARAMETERS show_subpos, show_marker show = show_subpos
tt = -0.003 rank = 0.006 if type_ogr = 1 then tf = 0.003 bf = 0.05 hf = 0.1 endif
if type_ogr = 2 then tf = 0.005 bf = 0.09 hf = 0.16 endif
if type_ogr = 3 then tf = 0.005 bf = 0.16 hf = 0.16 endif
if type_ogr = 4 then tf = 0.005 bf = 0.09 hf = 0.09 endif
np = CEIL(lrah-hroL-hroR) + 1 !if lrah < 1 then np = 2 !if (lrah >= 1) and (lrah < 2) then np = 3 parameters np = np post = 7850 parameters mater = 'С245', stal_marka = 'С245' parameters stal_gost = 'ГОСТ 27772-88'
obozn_tr = 'ГОСТ 30245-2012' obozn_pl = 'ГОСТ 19903-74' obozn_ank = 'ГОСТ 28778-90'
pos_1 = "1" tip_profile_1 = '60x40x3' obozn_1 = obozn_tr p_1 = (60*2+40*2)/1000 l1_1 = lrah vp_1 = 4.25 v1_1 = l1_1*vp_1
v_1 = ll_1*vp_1 s_1 = ll_1*p_1 naen_1 = tip_profile_1 + " L=" + str("%.0mm",l1_1)+"мм." kol_vo_spec_1 = 1
pos_2 = "2" tip_profile_2 = '50x3' obozn_2 = obozn_tr p_2 = (50*4)/1000 if (type_ogr = 4) or (type_ogr = 2) then dob = tf else dob = 0 endif l1_2 = hr + 0.14 + gs_PostBaseOverhang - hrh - dob vp_2 = 4.25 v1_2 = l1_2*vp_2 l_2 = np*l1_2 v_2 = vp_2*l_2 s_2 = l_2*p_2 naen_2 = tip_profile_2 + " L=" + str("%.0mm",l1_2)+"мм." kol_vo_spec_2 = np
pos_3 = "3" tip_profile_3 = '40x2' obozn_3 = obozn_tr p_3 = (40*4)/1000 if iInclinationMethod = 1 then l1_3 = lrah - hroL - hroR + addl + addr else l1_3 = lrah - hroLDiagonal - hroRDiagonal + addl + addr endif vp_3 = 2.31 v1_3 = l1_3*vp_3 l_3 = l1_3 v_3 = vp_3*l_3 s_3 = l_3*p_3 naen_3 = tip_profile_3 + " L=" + str("%.0mm",l1_3)+"мм." kol_vo_spec_3 = 1
pos_4 = "4" tip_profile_4 = '-- 3' obozn_4 = obozn_pl p_4 = 0.14*2 l1_4 = lrah - hroL - hroR + addl2 + addr2 vp_4 = 0.003*post v1_4 = 0.14*l1_4*vp_4 l_4 = l1_4 v_4 = 0.14*vp_4*l_4 s_4 = p_4 * l_4 naen_4 = "-- 3x140x"+str("%.0mm",l1_4) kol_vo_spec_4 = 1
pos_5 = "5" tip_profile_5 = '-- 3' obozn_5 = obozn_pl t5 = 0.003 b5 = pw + 2 * tt h5 = pw + 2 * tt s_5 = b5*h5*2*np v1_5 = t5*b5*h5*post vp_5 = t5*post v_5 = v1_5 * np l_5 = b5 * np l1_5 = b5 * h5 naen_5 = "-- 3х" + str("%.0mm",b5)+"х"+str("%.0mm",h5) kol_vo_spec_5 = np
pos_6 = "6" s_6 = bf*hf*2 v1_6 = tf*bf*hf*post vp_6 = tf*post v_6 = v1_6 * np l_6 = bf*hf obozn_6 = obozn_pl tip_profile_6 = '-- '+ str("%.0mm",tf) ll_6 = bf * hf naen_6 = "--" + str("%.0mm",tf)+"х"+str("%.0mm",bf)+"х"+str("%.0mm",hf) kol_vo_spec_6 = np
pos_7 = "7" s_7 = bf*hf*2 v1_7 = tf*bf*hf*post vp_7 = tf*post v_7 = v1_7 l_7 = bf obozn_7 = obozn_pl tip_profile_7 = '-- '+ str("%.0mm",tf) ll_7 = bf * hf naen_7 = "--" + str("%.0mm",tf)+"х"+str("%.0mm",bf)+"х"+str("%.0mm",hf) kol_vo_spec_7 = np
pos_8 = "8" v1_8 = 0.134 obozn_8 = obozn_ank naen_8="Болт распорный М12х110" kol_vo_spec_8 = 4*np v_8 = v1_8 * kol_vo_spec_8
pos_9 = "9" s_9 = bf*hf*2 v1_9 = tf*bf*hf*post vp_9 = tf*post v_9 = v1_9*np l_9 = bf*hf obozn_9 = obozn_pl tip_profile_9 = '-- '+ str("%.0mm",tf) ll_9 = bf * hf naen_9 = "--" + str("%.0mm",tf)+"х"+str("%.0mm",bf)+"х"+str("%.0mm",hf) kol_vo_spec_9 = np
pos_10 = "10" s_10 = bf*hf*2 v1_10 = tf*bf*hf*post vp_10 = tf*post v_10 = v1_10 l_10 = bf obozn_10 = obozn_pl tip_profile_10 = '-- '+ str("%.0mm",tf) l1_10 = bf * hf naen_10 = "--" + str("%.0mm",tf)+"х"+str("%.0mm",bf)+"х"+str("%.0mm",hf) kol_vo_spec_10 = np
spokr = s_1 + s_2 + s_3 ves = v_1 + v_2 + v_3
if (type_ogr = 1) or (type_ogr = 3) or (type_ogr = 5) then spokr = spokr + s_5 ves = ves + v_5 endif if type_ogr = 1 then spokr = spokr + s_10 ves = ves + v_10 endif if type_ogr = 2 then spokr = spokr + s_9 ves = ves + v_8 + v_9 endif if type_ogr = 3 then spokr = spokr + s_7 ves = ves + v_8 + v_7 endif if type_ogr = 4 then spokr = spokr + s_6 ves = ves + v_6 endif if type_ogr = 5 then spokr = spokr + s_6 ves = ves + v_6 endif if rom = "Нет наклона" then spokr = spokr + s_4 ves = ves + v_4 endif
parameters spokr = spokr + spokr * 0.001 parameters ves = ves + ves * 0.071 ! ============================================================================== ! Rail Wired ! ==============================================================================
EPS = 0.0001
modInclAngle = ani if iInclinationMethod = 1 then modInclAngle = 0 if show then call "m_Rail Wired_mod" parameters all ani = modInclAngle
Symbol.Script_PR:
call "Спецификатор" parameters tip_el='45', subpos = subpos, obozn=obozn, naen=naen, kol_vo_spec=1, komment=" ", otm_elem=ac_bottomlevel+SYMB_POS_Z gosub "1" gosub "2" gosub "3" if rom = "Нет наклона" then gosub "4"
if type_ogr = 1 then gosub "5" gosub "10" endif
if type_ogr = 2 then gosub "9" gosub "8" endif
if type_ogr = 3 then gosub "5" gosub "7" gosub "8" endif
if type_ogr = 4 then gosub "6"
if type_ogr = 5 then gosub "5"
tip_el = "30" komment = "кв.м." obozn = "см. примечания" naen = "Покрытие " + mat_pokr kol_vo_spec = spokr
call "Спецификатор" parameters tip_el=tip_el, subpos = subpos, obozn=obozn, naen=naen, kol_vo_spec=spokr, komment=komment, otm_elem=ac_bottomlevel+SYMB_POS_Z goto 20
"1": pos = pos_1 obozn = obozn_1 tip_profile = tip_profile_1 dlin_prof = l1_1 ves = vp_1 kol_vo_spec = kol_vo_spec_1 naen = naen_1 gosub "spec_m" return
"2": pos = pos_2 obozn = obozn_2 dlin_prof = l1_2 tip_profile = tip_profile_2 ves = vp_2 kol_vo_spec = kol_vo_spec_2 naen = naen_2 gosub "spec_m" return
"3": pos = pos_3 obozn = obozn_3 tip_profile = tip_profile_3 dlin_prof = l1_3 ves = vp_3 kol_vo_spec = kol_vo_spec_3 naen = naen_3 gosub "spec_m" return
"4": pos = pos_4 obozn = obozn_4 tip_profile = tip_profile_4 dlin_prof = 0.14*l1_4 kol_vo_spec = kol_vo_spec_4 ves = vp_4 naen = naen_4 if type_spec = "Металл" then gosub "spec_m" else gosub "spec_i" endif return
"5": pos = pos_5 obozn = obozn_5 tip_profile = tip_profile_5 dlin_prof = l1_5 kol_vo_spec = kol_vo_spec_5 naen = naen_5 if type_spec = "Металл" then ves = vp_5 gosub "spec_m" else ves = v1_5 gosub "spec_i" endif return
"6": pos = pos_6 obozn = obozn_6 kol_vo_spec = kol_vo_spec_6 dlin_prof = l1_6 naen = naen_6 if type_spec = "Металл" then tip_profile = tip_profile_6 ves = vp_6 gosub "spec_m" else ves = v1_6 gosub "spec_i" endif return
"7": pos = pos_7 obozn = obozn_7 dlin_prof = l1_7 kol_vo_spec = kol_vo_spec_7 naen = naen_7 if type_spec = "Металл" then tip_profile = tip_profile_7 ves = vp_7 gosub "spec_m" else ves = v1_7 gosub "spec_i" endif return
"8": pos = pos_8 obozn = obozn_8 if type_spec <> "Металл" then naen = naen_8 ves = v1_8 kol_vo_spec = kol_vo_spec_8 gosub "spec_i" endif return
"9": pos = pos_9 obozn = obozn_9 dlin_prof = l1_9 kol_vo_spec = kol_vo_spec_9 naen = naen_9 if type_spec = "Металл" then tip_profile = tip_profile_9 ves = vp_9 gosub "spec_m" else ves = v1_9 gosub "spec_i" endif return
"10": pos = pos_10 obozn = obozn_10 dlin_prof = l1_10 kol_vo_spec = kol_vo_spec_10 naen = naen_10 if type_spec = "Металл" then tip_profile = tip_profile_10 ves = vp_10 gosub "spec_m" else ves = v1_10 gosub "spec_i" endif return
"spec_m": tip_el = "20" call "Спецификатор" parameters tip_el=tip_el, subpos = subpos, pos = pos, tip_konstr=tip_konstr, stal_gost=stal_gost, mater=mater, obozn=obozn, tip_profile=tip_profile, dlin_prof=dlin_prof, ves=ves, naen=naen, otm_elem=ac_bottomlevel+SYMB_POS_Z, kol_vo_spec = kol_vo_spec return
"spec_i": tip_el = "40" if pos = "4" then k = "п.м." else k = " " endif call "Спецификатор" parameters tip_el=tip_el, subpos = subpos, pos = pos, obozn=obozn, naen=naen, ves=ves, kol_vo_spec=kol_vo_spec, komment=k, otm_elem=ac_bottomlevel+SYMB_POS_Z return 20:

Symbol.Script_FWM:
actualGUID = FROM_GUID
! ============================================================================== ! "Inclination Method", "Measurement Method" parameter setting (AC15 --> AC16) ! ==============================================================================
if actualGuid = "228C59D5-18C6-4D54-9E27-DC9AF99BCE11" then call "railMigration_m" parameters iObjectType = 11, iMigrationStep = 1, iInclinationMethod = iInclinationMethod, rom_m = rom_m, rmm_m = rmm_m, ani = ani, returned_parameters returnedActID, iInclinationMethod, rom_m, rmm_m, dummyParam
if returnedActID = 1 then actualGuid = "C925715E-1A44-4A64-A528-D387CBC3330B" else actualGuid = "" endif endif

SETMIGRATIONGUID actualGUID
Symbol.Script_BWM:
bContinue = 1
! ============================================================================== ! "Inclination Angle" parameter setting (AC16 --> AC15) ! ==============================================================================
if bContinue then call "railMigration_m" parameters iObjectType = 11, iMigrationStep = 1, iInclinationMethod = iInclinationMethod, ani = ani, returned_parameters returnedTargetID, ani, dummyParam
if returnedTargetID = 1 then targetGuid = "228C59D5-18C6-4D54-9E27-DC9AF99BCE11" else targetGuid = "" bContinue = 0 endif if TO_GUID = "228C59D5-18C6-4D54-9E27-DC9AF99BCE11" then bContinue = 0 endif
! ============================================================================== ! Set migration GUID ! ==============================================================================
SETMIGRATIONGUID targetGuid
